Minimum and Maximum
Find the difference between the min and max values of 
1. each row of a matrix
2. the whole matrix


function [mmr,mmm]=minimax(A)
mmt=[max(A,[],2)-min(A,[],2)];
mmr=mmt'
mmm=max(A,[],"all")-min(A,[],"all")


mmr =

     3     3     3


mmm =

    11




https://www.mathworks.com/help/matlab/ref/max.html
